PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FUnder-16s should be banned from social
OL,7,Fmedia as platforms either cannot or
OL,8,Fwill not regulate content well enough
OL,9,Fand the UK lacks the manpower to force
OL,10,Fthem to do so, the reviewer of
OL,11,Fterrorism laws has said.
OL,13,FJonathan Hall KC told the Press
OL,14,FAssociation that the online world
OL,15,Fshould be at the front and centre of
OL,16,Fall national security decisions, as
OL,17,Fchildren spend hours every day online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FLonely and isolated children can find
OL,7,F"a huge sense of meaning" by
OL,8,Fconnecting with others in a digital
OL,9,Fworld but are more at risk of being
OL,10,Fdrawn into extremism, he said.
OL,12,FMr Hall's comments came as
OL,13,Finternational study by the Global
OL,14,FTerrorism Index found that multiplayer
OL,15,Fgames, and social media apps used by
OL,16,Fgamers, are being exploited by
OL,17,Fpredators who want to radicalise young
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FSteve Killelea, head of think-tank the
OL,7,FInstitute for Economics and Peace,
OL,8,Fwhich publishes the Index, said: "One
OL,9,Fof the most alarming developments in
OL,10,Fyouth radicalisation is the
OL,11,Fweaponisation of online gaming and
OL,12,Fgaming-adjacent communication
OL,13,Fplatforms, including Discord, Twitch,
OL,14,FSteam, and Roblox.
OL,16,F"Multiplayer gaming environments
OL,17,Fprovide ideal digital infrastructure
OL,18,Ffor isolation, alternative community
OL,19,Fbuilding, and the normalisation of
OL,20,Fviolence.
OL,26,@pD@bOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,F"Recruiters leveraged popular
OL,7,Fmultiplayer games, including
OL,8,FMinecraft, Fortnite, and Call of Duty,
OL,9,Fto establish social bonds with
OL,10,Fisolated adolescents under the guise
OL,11,Fof shared recreational interests.
OL,13,F"This gamification extended to the
OL,14,Fcreation of bespoke extremist
OL,15,Fmodifications and custom servers where
OL,16,Fusers actively role-played violent
OL,17,Ffantasies.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,F"Minors have been documented using
OL,7,Fsimulation games to digitally rehearse
OL,8,Freal-world violence, such as simulated
OL,9,Fattacks on mosques, synagogues, or
OL,10,Fschools, blurring the cognitive
OL,11,Fboundary between digital recreation
OL,12,Fand physical terrorism.
OL,14,F"The gamification of extremism has
OL,15,Falso extended to the creation of
OL,16,F'scoreboards' and competitive dynamics
OL,17,Fwithin extremist communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,F"Online forums tracked and celebrated
OL,7,Fthe 'kill counts' of mass attackers,
OL,8,Fcreating perverse incentive structures
OL,9,Fthat encouraged escalation.
OL,11,F"For adolescents already immersed in
OL,12,Fcompetitive gaming cultures, these
OL,13,Fdynamics exploited familiar
OL,14,Fpsychological reward mechanisms:
OL,15,Fachievement, ranking, and peer
OL,16,Frecognition, to normalise and
OL,17,Fincentivise real-world violence."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FMr Hall said he wants policy and law
OL,7,Fenforcement officials to have more
OL,8,Fcontact with young extremists to
OL,9,Funderstand what pulls them "down the
OL,10,Frabbit hole".
OL,12,F"If you look at the Ofcom surveys
OL,13,Fabout how long children spend online,
OL,14,Fthey're spending six, seven, eight
OL,15,Fhours a day online.
OL,17,F"We know that there is a particular
OL,18,Fprofile of person at the moment who is
OL,19,Fgetting pulled into radicalisation.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@LO]tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,F"They're often friendless, with a high
OL,7,Finstance of autism, very unhappy,
OL,8,Flonely individuals who then find a
OL,9,Fhuge sense of meaning online.
OL,11,F"We need to get out of the habit of
OL,12,Fthinking about the online world as an
OL,13,Fextra. It needs to be front and centre
OL,14,Fof everything, of all national
OL,15,Fsecurity decisions.
OL,17,F"I would like to see a lot more
OL,18,Fcontact between policy officials and
OL,19,Fthe children who are most at risk of
OL,20,Fbeing drawn in.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,F"Not everyone who sees this stuff
OL,7,Fonline is going to be attracted by it,
OL,8,Fbut there are a number of people who,
OL,9,Fif you say, look at this person, he's
OL,10,Fkilled 52 people in a massacre in New
OL,11,FZealand, they'll go: 'Great. I'd like
OL,12,Fto do that.'
OL,14,F"We need to know more about those
OL,15,Fpeople and their experiences and what
OL,16,Fmight stop them going down the rabbit
OL,17,Fhole. We don't really talk to them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FTrying to moderate online content is
OL,7,Ftoo massive a task, the terror laws
OL,8,Fwatchdog said, meaning a social media
OL,9,Fban for under-16s should be introduced.
OL,11,FEarlier this month, a ban was rejected
OL,12,Fby the House of Commons, however, MPs
OL,13,Fbacked plans to give the secretary of
OL,14,Fstate more powers, meaning that in
OL,15,Ffuture Science Secretary Liz Kendall
OL,16,Fcould "restrict or ban children of
OL,17,Fcertain ages from accessing social
OL,18,Fmedia services and chat bots".
OL,26,@xD@GOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FMr Hall said: "My own personal view is
OL,7,Fthat under-16s should be off social
OL,8,Fmedia. The alternative is to try and
OL,9,Fregulate content, and that is so
OL,10,Fdifficult, it's so imperfect, trying
OL,11,Fto regulate content.
OL,13,F"The job is just too massive. If you
OL,14,Frely upon platforms, they either won't
OL,15,Fdo it or they won't be able to do it
OL,16,Fwell enough, because the volume of
OL,17,Fcontent is so high.
OL,26,@nD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,F"If you rely upon Ofcom, they've only
OL,7,Fgot 50 people in their enforcement
OL,8,Fteam. That's a tiny number of people
OL,9,Fto take action against recalcitrants.
OL,10,FAnd then you've got all sorts of
OL,11,Fplatforms based overseas who don't
OL,12,Fnecessarily care at all.
OL,14,F"Content moderation is just not going
OL,15,Fto deal with this, and the risks are
OL,16,Fso high, and the benefits are so
OL,17,Fdubious, of children watching what
OL,18,Fthey call brain rot."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FAn Ofcom spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,FGovernment is leading an important
OL,8,Fdebate on this, which we'll be
OL,9,Fsupporting with our independent expert
OL,10,Fadvice and insights from our research.
OL,12,F"In the meantime, we're getting on
OL,13,Fwith the job we've been given by
OL,14,FParliament ` to implement and enforce
OL,15,Fthe Online Safety Act ` and change is
OL,16,Fhappening."
OL,18,FThere have been concerns about the
OL,19,Fproportion of suspects arrested for
OL,20,Fterrorism offences in England and
OL,21,FWales who are under the age of 18.
OL,26,@nD@]OUtD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773806609
OL,3,CTerror laws watchdog: under-16s should
OL,4,Cbe off social media
OL,6,FIn 2025, 39 out of 255 suspects
OL,7,Farrested were aged under 18, and in
OL,8,F2024 40 out of 250.
OL,10,FThe Global Terrorism Index, due to be
OL,11,Fpublished on Thursday, found that in
OL,12,F2025, minors accounted for 42 percent
OL,13,Fof terror-related investigations in
OL,14,FEurope and North America, a three-fold
OL,15,Fincrease since 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
